### Data Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant ResultPage
    participant ChatbotPage
    participant FlaskBackend
    participant OllamaLLM

    User->>ResultPage: Taps "Ask" button
    ResultPage->>ChatbotPage: Navigator.pushNamed('/chatbot', args: PredictionResult)
    ChatbotPage->>ChatbotPage: Shows context banner with prediction summary
    User->>ChatbotPage: Types "Explain the result"
    ChatbotPage->>FlaskBackend: POST /api/chat {message, history, predictionContext}
    FlaskBackend->>OllamaLLM: Forward to qwen2.5:3b with system prompt + context
    OllamaLLM-->>FlaskBackend: LLM response
    FlaskBackend-->>ChatbotPage: {reply, source: "local"}
    ChatbotPage-->>User: Displays AI response bubble
```

